########################################################################
###########         HOW TO USE SV UNIT 		########################
########################################################################

Step 1: Source VCS script . SV unit uses the VCS simulator

Step 2: Source the Setup.csh file in the svunit folder.Make sure the SV unit path is set appropriately.

Step 3: set the ASE_WORKDIR path -> point it to the ase directory.
 
Step 4: make sim ----- Runs the VCS simulator and checks the SV unit test cases against the Design

Step 5: For Coverage , use make wave .
